## Troubleshooting

### Migration fallita

```bash
supabase db diff          # Vedi differenze
supabase migration list   # Lista migrations
supabase db reset         # Reset DB locale (SOLO sviluppo)
```

### Types non aggiornati

```bash
supabase gen types typescript --project-id <PROJECT_ID> \
  --schema public > packages/shared/src/types/database.ts
```
